Variable size reference:
Size of char: 1 byte, max = 255, min= 0
Size of short: 2 bytes, max = 32767, min= -32768
Size of int: 4 bytes, max = 2147483647, min= -2147483648
Size of long: 4 bytes, max = 2147483647, min= -2147483648
Size of long long: 8 bytes, max = 9223372036854775807, min= -9223372036854775808

